We just agreed that it's better
if we don't live together anymore. Okay?

74
00:08:19,165 --> 00:08:22,738
What do you look for
beyond the sea, Grasshopper?

75
00:08:24,103 --> 00:08:25,912
That part of me
which I know little of.

76
00:08:26,873 --> 00:08:29,353
The past of which I was born.

77
00:08:29,408 --> 00:08:31,752
Then, some day,
you must seek it.

78
00:08:32,111 --> 00:08:35,058
ls it good to seek the past,
Master Po?

79
00:08:36,949 --> 00:08:38,895
Does it not rob the present?

80
00:08:38,951 --> 00:08:42,296
If a man dwells on the past,
then he robs the present.

81
00:08:42,855 --> 00:08:46,769
