-Blow it up.
-Louder!

132
00:14:14,920 --> 00:14:16,365
-Blow it up.
-Louder!

133
00:14:16,589 --> 00:14:21,504
Blow it up! Blow it the fuck up! Blow it up!
Blow it up!

134
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:22,561
Right.

135
00:14:22,995 --> 00:14:24,497
Too right, mate.

136
00:14:24,763 --> 00:14:27,107
