138
00:14:32,872 --> 00:14:38,550
I'm the Beaver, Walter,
and I'm here to save your goddamn life.

139
00:14:44,183 --> 00:14:45,321
Hey.

140
00:14:46,018 --> 00:14:48,555
I'm sorry. I must have passed him again.
He just blends in.

141
00:14:48,621 --> 00:14:50,294
No, his dad picked him up early.

142
00:14:51,156 --> 00:14:52,157
Walter?

143
00:14:52,324 --> 00:14:57,103
He said he sent you a text.
Your husband is quite a character.

144
00:15:16,348 --> 00:15:18,021
Mom, you gotta see what we did.

145
00:15:18,083 --> 00:15:21,087
-Okay. Where's your father?
-Come on! I'll show you.

146
00:15:24,623 --> 00:15:26,034
You put your memory in it.

147
00:15:26,659 --> 00:15:28,195
Where'd you get that?

148
00:15:28,260 --> 00:15:30,399
-We made it.
-You and your dad?

149
00:15:30,963 --> 00:15:32,203
Me and the Beaver.

150
00:15:33,232 --> 00:15:34,609
-The Beaver?

151
00:15:40,105 --> 00:15:42,176
Any idea where Walter
stuffed the power sander

152
00:15:42,241 --> 00:15:44,016
you gave him two Christmases ago?

153
00:15:45,844 --> 00:15:46,845
No?

154
00:15:47,346 --> 00:15:49,383
No trouble. We'll make do.

155
00:15:49,481 --> 00:15:52,485
Walter, what's with the accent
and the puppet?

156
00:15:52,952 --> 00:15:55,125
-Give her the thing.
-Right.

157
00:16:00,159 --> 00:16:02,469
"Hello. The person
who handed you this card

158
00:16:02,528 --> 00:16:05,532
