159
00:16:06,031 --> 00:16:07,374
Walter, what the hell is this?

160
00:16:07,433 --> 00:16:10,903
Henry, mate, go see if you can find
that varnish we was talking about.

161
00:16:11,136 --> 00:16:13,241
-I'll get it!
-Thanks, mate!

162
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:16,717
