163
00:16:18,043 --> 00:16:20,080
-Yes, I...
-Read the card.

164
00:16:20,145 --> 00:16:22,056
-I've...
-Read the card.

165
00:16:26,285 --> 00:16:30,597
"The person who handed you this card
is under the care of a prescription puppet

166
00:16:30,656 --> 00:16:34,069
