178
00:17:10,029 --> 00:17:11,702
Well, I went back.

179
00:17:14,466 --> 00:17:18,107
So this is some kind of a program?

180
00:17:19,705 --> 00:17:23,050
I'll field that one. Yes, Meredith.
The answer is yes.

181
00:17:23,342 --> 00:17:25,219
That is exactly what it is.

182
00:17:25,277 --> 00:17:26,483
I know it seems radical,

183
00:17:26,612 --> 00:17:30,355
but in cases like Walter's,
cases where all else has been known to fail,

184
00:17:30,549 --> 00:17:32,426
it's proven quite effective.

185
00:17:33,218 --> 00:17:37,166
