-I'll come back this weekend, then.
-Come on.

196
00:17:59,144 --> 00:18:01,385
-It's okay. Just for dinner.
-Please, Mom.

197
00:18:02,281 --> 00:18:04,261
-Yeah!
-Well, right, then.

198
00:18:04,316 --> 00:18:06,455
Let's tidy up the garage
so we can mess up the kitchen.

199
