He thinks I'm going to fall for this?

204
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:30,517
-Who?
-Mumphry, or whatever

205
00:18:31,243 --> 00:18:33,052
vice-principal sent you.

206
00:18:33,345 --> 00:18:35,222
Tell him I'm insulted.

207
00:18:36,515 --> 00:18:40,088
Hey, will you hold on for a second?
No one sent me.

208
00:18:40,619 --> 00:18:42,121
I really need help.

209
