doesn't happen overnight.

244
00:20:53,619 --> 00:20:55,860
Still I can't believe
that you guys made that.

245
00:20:57,122 --> 00:20:59,932
I mean, you never... I mean, Walter never...

246
00:21:02,661 --> 00:21:05,904
