676
00:52:31,848 --> 00:52:34,454
I'm sorry, son. I didn't mean to do that.

677
00:52:34,518 --> 00:52:36,623
You keep your hands off him!

678
00:52:37,287 --> 00:52:38,595
Porter, come on. Let me see.

679
00:52:52,769 --> 00:52:54,077
