689
00:54:09,012 --> 00:54:10,286
I've got to hand it to you.

690
00:54:10,347 --> 00:54:13,556
You pulled all the strings,
and look where we landed.

691
00:54:13,617 --> 00:54:15,494
On top, for once.

692
00:54:19,956 --> 00:54:22,232
-It feels good, doesn't it?
-They.

693
00:54:26,329 --> 00:54:27,330
Sir?

694
00:54:28,898 --> 00:54:30,241
My family.

695
00:54:31,167 --> 00:54:33,738
Who's the biggest interview request
we've had so far?

696
00:54:36,640 --> 00:54:40,918
-All the morning shows. CNN, CNBC...
-Today Show, then. Set it up.

697
00:54:40,977 --> 00:54:44,754
But, sir, the Today Show is on television.

698
00:54:44,814 --> 00:54:51,197
What are we hiding? We're winners.
