see the bleeding expert.

723
00:56:48,405 --> 00:56:50,612
-Walter finally helped himself.
-Listen to yourself. This is insane.

724
00:56:50,673 --> 00:56:51,708
You're talking about a puppet.

725
00:56:51,775 --> 00:56:55,552
No, Meredith.
You're talking about a bloody puppet.

726
00:56:56,346 --> 00:56:58,587
We're talking about a miracle.

727
00:57:01,518 --> 00:57:03,225
-Who's "we," Walter?

728
00:57:11,995 --> 00:57:14,407
I know it's hard, mate. I know.

729
00:57:16,266 --> 00:57:18,473
You can't afford to get mixed up
in all of this.

730
00:57:19,969 --> 00:57:23,576
You just keep moving.
Keep moving and don't look back.

731
00:57:40,023 --> 00:57:42,003
You're right, of course.

732
00:57:43,960 --> 00:57:45,769
Walter is sick.

733
00:57:48,965 --> 00:57:54,074
But make no mistake about it, love.
I'm not going anywhere.

734
00:58:02,946 --> 00:58:04,721
I've rented a house.

735
00:58:05,915 --> 00:58:08,327
I'm taking the boys
and everything we can carry.

